{"tid":439391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[是咁的]小弟同巴打夾份開左間成人用品店 想做返折頭益所有巴打","createTime":"2017-10-17T18:02:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-17T20:37:51.000Z","uid":124519,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d2afd413575599e1ad6e1bb1e4efb35cbe988752","tid":439391,"uid":124519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T18:02:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n小弟同另一位巴打上高登已經19幾年 <br />\n<br />\n後來連登開左就轉埋過黎<br />\n<br />\n咁最近我地夾份開左間成人用品店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n做折頭回贈返巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n能力內盡做   事關做零售拎貨好多時有set最低售價<br />\n<br />\n過左個數而我地又出左名俾人知就斷貨源  會出事<br />\n<br />\n網店:<a href=\"https://sexzonehk.shoplineapp.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsexzonehk.shoplineapp.com%2F&d=%2BStmu2oD2BmvbffMkvJrmYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=515c3a51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sexzonehk.shoplineapp.com/</a> <br />\nIG:<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sexzonehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fsexzonehk%2F&d=%2BStmu2oD2BmvbffMkvJrmYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=151f175b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/sexzonehk/</a> <br />\nFB:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sexzonehk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsexzonehk%2F&d=%2BStmu2oD2BmvbffMkvJrmYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=12a71606\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sexzonehk/</a> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過網站未完全ok 可能版面有時會轉下+有改動 FOR睇貨only <br />\n<br />\n如果想買野可以係網店直接做個order留個whatsapp溝通  但唔好過數/俾錢<br />\n<br />\n網站個價未有折<br />\n<br />\n我報返個價   order可以cancel的 唔洗怕醜<br />\n<br />\n又或者去IG PAGE<br />\n<br />\nPM我要D乜實際報價 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n付款方法:銀行過數(中銀/HSBC(過數記得要出返張入數紙!!)) <br />\n<br />\n送貨方法: <br />\n面交(旺角東鐵/地鐵站 免費) <br />\n<br />\n順豐 <br />\n-順豐站(運費: HK$20 / 單次消費滿$300免費) <br />\n-7仔/OK/智能櫃(運費: HK$30 / 單次消費滿$300免費) <br />\n-速遞上門(運費: HK$55 / 單次消費滿$500免費) <br />\n<br />\n暫定咁樣,,,同埋近幾日小弟都仲有地方傾緊貨搵緊貨 可能會效率慢少少 唔好介意 <br />\n有D咩貨你地有心水都可以同我講 <br />\n我睇下入唔入到 <br />\n<br />\np.s.折好似好少但本身定價低已經貼住市場上面有舖而開係工廠區ge網店 <br />\n當然D野有平有貴  如果外面有地方買的平過我/唔啱價可以照直講<br />\n買賣不成仁義在<br />\n<br />\n小弟間舖係旺角租金成本都有壓力  <br />\n希望大家理解同支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8f84ec58f9d3ba225057163ae069bda6bd733b","tid":439391,"uid":72228,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T18:13:09.000Z","msg":"仆街啦去賣廣告"},{"pid":"741c407d93791444c920b2e83554e4c152f63546","tid":439391,"uid":611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T18:16:06.000Z","msg":"Condom都無？"},{"pid":"88276a4b8d5a191f2f7a2b1416527886fe6639aa","tid":439391,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T18:16:13.000Z","msg":"老實講開po賣廣告講野咁得體<br />\n我buy喎<br />\n<br />\nbtw係連登賣成人用品會唔會渣兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11ad9fceaecf37456305c49d945618b279f6213b","tid":439391,"uid":124519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T18:17:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Condom都無？</blockquote><br />\n入左 未到貨  所以網站未上架"},{"pid":"2dc994c635953af47c423bd63cc04e1e6f7ac9ae","tid":439391,"uid":72228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T18:18:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老實講開po賣廣告講野咁得體<br />\n我buy喎<br />\n<br />\nbtw係連登賣成人用品會唔會渣兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點呀打手咁快開工？"},{"pid":"d85416934aa07bf8f79c05807cd6f6ee11804906","tid":439391,"uid":148749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-17T18:19:43.000Z","msg":"等我溝到條女就幫趁"},